data.description: Great 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home with a den, centrally located in Casa Grande. In addition to the 3 car garage this home also has an RV gate. Open floor plan flows into the dining area with plenty of windows around providing bright spaces. The adjoining kitchen has a breakfast bar, stainless steel appliances and an additional eat-in nook. Master bedroom suite features a separate shower & soaking tub, extended vanity counter space and a large walk-in closet. Step out onto the oversized, covered back patio and low maintenance backyard offering a sizeable grassy area and desert landscaping surrounding the lot edges. Home also has solar panels, providing a significant monthly savings in electric bills!
